700950f-a.title: Bronx: Tremont Avenue (East - Haskin Street
700950f-a.text:
East Tremont Ave., east side, south from but not including Haskin
Street, to Eastern Boulevard. The old 27i. -story frame house bears
No. 3379.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
